B.RQ=new A.dz('Privacy Policy\n\nLast updated: April 2026\n\nBAIT Studios ("we", "us") operates Line Crush!. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.\n\n1. Information We Collect\nLine Crush! does not require an account or personal information to play. We collect anonymous analytics data including session length, game events, and crash reports via Firebase Analytics.\n\n2. Advertising\nWe use Google AdMob for advertising. Our advertising partners may collect device identifiers and usage data to serve relevant ads. You can opt out of personalised ads in your device settings.\n\n3. Data Storage\nGame data (high scores, settings) is stored locally on your device and is not transmitted to our servers.\n\n4. Children\'s Privacy\nLine Crush! is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from children.\n\n5. Changes to This Policy\nWe may update this Privacy Policy at any time. Changes take effect when posted.\n\n6. Contact\nFor privacy questions, contact hello@bait.name.',null,B.yg,null,null)
